## 6. Image Handling

### 6.1 Sourcing

Mark has explicit permission to use all images from both partner sites. Download the following:

**From thewindchime.co:**
- Hero/lifestyle image of wind chime (for page hero and services card)
- Individual product images for the 6 featured wind chimes
- Company logo

**From usmetalcraft.com:**
- Category images for vases (upright, ground, wall mount, replacement)
- Category images for urns (aria, traditional, cloisonne, flag, wood, keepsakes)
- Category images for accessories (memorial lights, emblems, bouquets, flag holder)
- Company logo
- "Made in USA" badge

### 6.2 Storage

Save all images in the `/public` directory following the existing naming convention:

```
public/
  wind-chimes/
    hero.png (or .jpg)
    whispering-hearts-platinum.png
    whispering-hearts-rosegold.png
    serenity-amazing-grace.png
    serenity-church-bells.png
