## 7. Component Specifications

### 7.1 ProductCard

Reusable card for individual products (used for wind chimes):

```typescript
interface ProductCardProps {
  name: string;
  description: string;
  imageSrc: string;
  imageAlt: string;
  size?: string; // e.g., "30 inches"
  features?: string[]; // bullet points
}
```

Visual: Same card style as the statue option cards on `/statues`. Image on top, content below. No price. No "Add to cart" button. Hover animation consistent with existing cards.

### 7.2 CategoryCard

Reusable card for product categories (used for vases, urns, accessories):

```typescript
interface CategoryCardProps {
  name: string;
  description: string;
  imageSrc: string;
  imageAlt: string;
}
```

Visual: Same as the service cards on the `/services` page. Image, title, short description. These are NOT clickable links to sub-pages (there are no sub-pages). They're display-only cards showing what's available.

### 7.3 PartnerBadges

Two side-by-side cards showing partner info. Follow the "Featured artists and collections" pattern from `/statues`:

```typescript
interface PartnerBadgeProps {
  name: string;
  description: string;
  logoSrc: string;
  logoAlt: string;
  badge?: string; // e.g., "Made in USA"
}
```

