## 8. Responsive Behavior

Follow the same responsive breakpoints as other service pages:

- **Desktop (1024px+):** 3-column product grid, 2-column partner badges
- **Tablet (768px - 1023px):** 2-column product grid, stacked partner badges
- **Mobile (< 768px):** 1-column everything, stacked CTAs

---

## 9. Animations

Use Framer Motion consistent with the rest of the site:
- Fade-in on scroll for sections
- Staggered card entrance animations (same as services page cards)
- Hover scale on cards (same as existing cards)

Do NOT add any new animation patterns. Match exactly what exists.

